[
	{
		"id": 0,
		"localized_name": "ユリエ",
		"romanized_name": "Jurie",
		"model_path_hash": "6932496336129827816",
		"text": "ミルカ。ヴィアベル州に残って、\nシャリーたちと水遊びしなくてよかったの？",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "8415011553540267009",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 1,
		"localized_name": "ミルカ",
		"romanized_name": "Miruca",
		"model_path_hash": "6658023269359396885",
		"text": "私はこの旅に目的があるから、いいの。\nシャリーたちと遊ぶのは今じゃなくてもできるし",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "1034358740077913276",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 2,
		"localized_name": "ミルカ",
		"romanized_name": "Miruca",
		"model_path_hash": "6658023269359396885",
		"text": "それにもうハイネ州まで来ちゃったもの。\n今さら戻ってもおかしいでしょ",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "1034358740077913276",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 3,
		"localized_name": "ユリエ",
		"romanized_name": "Jurie",
		"model_path_hash": "6932496336129827816",
		"text": "……そうね、分かった。\nここは暑いから、体調には気を付けて",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "8415011553540267009",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 4,
		"localized_name": "ミルカ",
		"romanized_name": "Miruca",
		"model_path_hash": "0",
		"text": "（この辺りの地層、資料と違う……\n　採取したい鉱石が、見当たらない……）",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "1034358740077913276",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 5,
		"localized_name": "ユリエ",
		"romanized_name": "Jurie",
		"model_path_hash": "6932496336129827816",
		"text": "探してる素材、見つからない？",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "8415011553540267009",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 6,
		"localized_name": "ミルカ",
		"romanized_name": "Miruca",
		"model_path_hash": "6658023269359396885",
		"text": "うん。もう少し奥まで行けば、あるかも",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "1034358740077913276",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 7,
		"localized_name": "ユリエ",
		"romanized_name": "Jurie",
		"model_path_hash": "6932496336129827816",
		"text": "分かった。ただ安全第一にね。\n火山は危ない場所よ",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "8415011553540267009",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 8,
		"localized_name": "ミルカ",
		"romanized_name": "Miruca",
		"model_path_hash": "6658023269359396885",
		"text": "分かってる。\n……姉さんがいるから、平気",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "1034358740077913276",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 9,
		"localized_name": "ユリエ",
		"romanized_name": "Jurie",
		"model_path_hash": "6932496336129827816",
		"text": "そう言ってもらえると嬉しいわ",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "8415011553540267009",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 10,
		"localized_name": "ミルカ",
		"romanized_name": "Miruca",
		"model_path_hash": "6658023269359396885",
		"text": "別に、深い意味はない",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "1034358740077913276",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 11,
		"localized_name": "ミルカ",
		"romanized_name": "Miruca",
		"model_path_hash": "0",
		"text": "（あれも違う……どれも……）",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "1034358740077913276",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 12,
		"localized_name": "ユリエ",
		"romanized_name": "Jurie",
		"model_path_hash": "6932496336129827816",
		"text": "焦らなくていい。\n素材はきっと見つかるわ",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "8415011553540267009",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 13,
		"localized_name": "ミルカ",
		"romanized_name": "Miruca",
		"model_path_hash": "6658023269359396885",
		"text": "根拠もなく、そんなことを言わないで",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "1034358740077913276",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 14,
		"localized_name": "ユリエ",
		"romanized_name": "Jurie",
		"model_path_hash": "6932496336129827816",
		"text": "根拠ならある。\nミルカはとっても優秀だから。私が保証する",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "8415011553540267009",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 15,
		"localized_name": "ミルカ",
		"romanized_name": "Miruca",
		"model_path_hash": "6658023269359396885",
		"text": "……姉さん、ちょっと静かにして",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "1034358740077913276",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 16,
		"localized_name": "レジナ",
		"romanized_name": "Regina",
		"model_path_hash": "6530292426083289682",
		"text": "やっほー！　\nこんな所でなにしてるの？",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "5764066045850619995",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 17,
		"localized_name": "ユリエ",
		"romanized_name": "Jurie",
		"model_path_hash": "6932496336129827816",
		"text": "あら、レジナ。久しぶりね。\n私たちはちょっと探しものを。あなたは？",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "8415011553540267009",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 18,
		"localized_name": "レジナ",
		"romanized_name": "Regina",
		"model_path_hash": "6530292426083289682",
		"text": "わたしは発掘屋だからね、火山の鉱脈を調査中！\nところで二人の探しものってなに？",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "5764066045850619995",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 19,
		"localized_name": "ミルカ",
		"romanized_name": "Miruca",
		"model_path_hash": "6658023269359396885",
		"text": "……鉱石。\nこの火山固有の、特殊な成分のもの",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "1034358740077913276",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 20,
		"localized_name": "レジナ",
		"romanized_name": "Regina",
		"model_path_hash": "6530292426083289682",
		"text": "へえ～、それなら一緒に探そうか？　\n発掘屋の勘、なかなか当たるよ",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "5764066045850619995",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 21,
		"localized_name": "ユリエ",
		"romanized_name": "Jurie",
		"model_path_hash": "6932496336129827816",
		"text": "それは心強いわ。\nミルカ、どうする？",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "8415011553540267009",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 22,
		"localized_name": "ミルカ",
		"romanized_name": "Miruca",
		"model_path_hash": "6658023269359396885",
		"text": "……別に、断る理由はない",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "1034358740077913276",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 23,
		"localized_name": "レジナ",
		"romanized_name": "Regina",
		"model_path_hash": "6530292426083289682",
		"text": "決まり！　その鉱石、この辺りにはなかったんだよね？\nじゃ、あっちの岩場を見に行こう",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "5764066045850619995",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 24,
		"localized_name": "ユリエ",
		"romanized_name": "Jurie",
		"model_path_hash": "6932496336129827816",
		"text": "ミルカ、この先はもっと暑くなるだろうから、\n体調に気を付けて、何かあったら無理せず言うのよ",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "8415011553540267009",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 25,
		"localized_name": "ミルカ",
		"romanized_name": "Miruca",
		"model_path_hash": "6658023269359396885",
		"text": "分かってる……\n何度も言われなくても大丈夫だから",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "1034358740077913276",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 26,
		"localized_name": "ユリエ",
		"romanized_name": "Jurie",
		"model_path_hash": "6932496336129827816",
		"text": "そうね。でも、心配だから。\nほら、足元も険しくなってる。気を付けて",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "8415011553540267009",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 27,
		"localized_name": "ミルカ",
		"romanized_name": "Miruca",
		"model_path_hash": "6658023269359396885",
		"text": "……もう、分かってるってば",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "1034358740077913276",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 28,
		"localized_name": "レジナ",
		"romanized_name": "Regina",
		"model_path_hash": "6530292426083289682",
		"text": "ふふ、仲良し姉妹だね～",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "5764066045850619995",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 29,
		"localized_name": "ミルカ",
		"romanized_name": "Miruca",
		"model_path_hash": "6658023269359396885",
		"text": "……からかわないで",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "1034358740077913276",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 30,
		"localized_name": "レジナ・カティス",
		"romanized_name": "Regina Curtis",
		"model_path_hash": "0",
		"text": "腕利きの発掘屋。\n面倒見がよくしっかり者で、力仕事が得意",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "5764066045850619995",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	}
]